the most selfish, immature--

242
00:19:29,669 --> 00:19:31,920
-Wait, l'm seIfish?
-Yeah. Stubborn.

243
00:19:32,088 --> 00:19:34,548
-I'm immature?
-I don't know. That's what she says.

244
00:19:34,715 --> 00:19:36,508
You know what? Forget it. Okay?

245
00:19:36,676 --> 00:19:39,177
I'm not even gonna
dignify that with-- Whatever.

246
00:19:39,345 --> 00:19:41,763
Oh, yeah.
Hey, look, l'm on your team, man.

247
00:19:41,931 --> 00:19:45,517
