263
00:20:54,587 --> 00:20:57,339
-Stolen plates.
-Yeah, well, that's what I'm thinking.

264
00:20:57,506 --> 00:21:01,217
Look, if I hear anything on the kid
I'll let you know, but you...

265
00:21:01,385 --> 00:21:04,429
-...be careful, okay?
-Okay, great. Bobby, thanks.

266
00:21:37,546 --> 00:21:40,215
More pink, Tony.
Way the hell more pink.

267
00:21:40,383 --> 00:21:43,677
I wanna sparkle
with the illusion of youth.

268
00:21:43,886 --> 00:21:46,221
