wanting to be loved by her man.

283
00:22:34,186 --> 00:22:37,022
I mean, come on.
Such a beautifuI couple...

284
00:22:37,189 --> 00:22:39,315
...and you threw it away.

285
00:22:40,026 --> 00:22:42,027
