336
00:25:59,016 --> 00:26:01,267
Tell you what.
You wanna make a break for it...

337
00:26:01,435 --> 00:26:03,853
...l will give you
a 1 0-second head start.

338
00:26:04,021 --> 00:26:07,649
-I am an adult, Milo. I'm--
-Ten.

339
00:26:07,816 --> 00:26:09,692
-Nine. Eight.
