Hey, Mi-- Hey!

369
00:28:16,153 --> 00:28:19,822
Oh, my God. I'm gonna have
a panic attack. Oh, my God. MiIo!

370
00:28:19,990 --> 00:28:22,950
Milo. Goddamn it!
Open this trunk, Milo.

371
00:28:23,118 --> 00:28:24,911
Right now. Milo.

372
00:28:25,079 --> 00:28:27,705
Okay. Okay.

373
00:28:30,584 --> 00:28:33,795
Yeah, l've got
a couple of small tats myself.

374
00:28:34,713 --> 00:28:38,257
But l'm still amazed at the level of pain
