386
00:29:18,799 --> 00:29:21,342
Oh, come on, Teresa, it's me.
You know it's me.

387
00:29:21,510 --> 00:29:24,679
-Hey, I need to taIk to Sid.
-Yeah, Sid's not available right now.

388
