400
00:30:10,559 --> 00:30:13,936
-...and that didn't pan out, either.
-He doesn't really seem your type.

401
00:30:14,104 --> 00:30:18,107
Listen. Okay, Milo, please. Please.

402
00:30:18,275 --> 00:30:20,985
