and watch nature take its course.

411
00:30:47,262 --> 00:30:52,016
-HeIlo?
-You stop.

412
00:30:52,184 --> 00:30:53,601
Hello?

413
00:30:54,770 --> 00:30:56,437
Nic?

414
00:30:57,147 --> 00:30:58,272
Nicole?

415
00:30:59,733 --> 00:31:00,816
