421
00:31:17,000 --> 00:31:18,584
God, Milo!

422
00:31:18,752 --> 00:31:21,587
-Do you hear the tone of my voice?
-Oh, God. So good.

423
00:31:21,755 --> 00:31:27,426
Milo! Oh, shoot. MiIo? Milo?

424
00:31:28,929 --> 00:31:31,013
Hello, NicoIe Hurley.

425
00:31:31,181 --> 00:31:32,723
Hey, hey, it's me. Jimmy.

426
