Jimmy. Oh, my God.

427
00:31:35,185 --> 00:31:37,228
Oh, my God, Jimmy,
I thought you were dead.

428
00:31:37,396 --> 00:31:41,691
Where are you?
I've Ieft you like 40 messages.

429
