432
00:31:48,490 --> 00:31:53,786
Oh, nothing. My friend showed up,
and he needed my help with something.

433
00:31:53,954 --> 00:31:55,955
Was that before
he busted your window?

434
00:31:56,164 --> 00:31:58,708
I locked my keys in--
Whatever. It's a piece of shit.

435
00:31:58,875 --> 00:32:02,253
Listen, hey, where are you?
You sound like you're in a closet.

436
00:32:02,796 --> 00:32:06,591
I'm-- I'm in Atlantic City.

437
00:32:06,800 --> 00:32:11,304
Listen, Jimmy, I went to your apartment,
and l found the coaster.

438
00:32:11,471 --> 00:32:14,724
Has there been evidence stolen
from the depository?

439
00:32:14,891 --> 00:32:17,518
Well, that's kind of why I'm calling.

440
00:32:17,686 --> 00:32:20,688
The whole thing turned out
to be nothing but a waste of time...

441
00:32:20,856 --> 00:32:24,233
-...for everybody involved.
-Who else is involved, Jimmy?

442
00:32:25,902 --> 00:32:26,944
Very good.

443
00:32:27,112 --> 00:32:29,322
Jimmy-- Jimmy?

444
00:32:30,032 --> 00:32:32,116
Listen, I need a favour.

445
00:32:32,618 --> 00:32:34,952
Nicole Hurley, 1 34 Perry Street.

446
