447
00:32:38,040 --> 00:32:40,625
Beautiful. Thanks.

448
00:32:51,470 --> 00:32:52,637
Nic?

449
00:33:21,166 --> 00:33:25,795
-What the hell happened to you?
-Milo Boyd. Asshole head-butted me.

450
