452
00:33:32,094 --> 00:33:33,594
Ray!

453
00:33:34,513 --> 00:33:37,098
Milo Boyd. Ex-cop.

454
00:33:37,265 --> 00:33:39,392
Fired last year for neglect of duty.

455
00:33:39,559 --> 00:33:42,436
His current gambIing debt
is just over 1 1 grand.

456
00:33:42,604 --> 00:33:45,856
We haven't seen a penny
in two months.

457
00:33:46,692 --> 00:33:47,900
This is not good.

458
00:33:48,068 --> 00:33:51,987
We Iet this bum slide, people gonna
start thinking Irene's gone soft...

459
00:33:52,155 --> 00:33:53,823
...they don't have to pay up.

460
00:33:54,366 --> 00:33:57,243
Get him in here, Dwight,
break some part of his person...

461
00:33:57,411 --> 00:34:00,496
